data.description: What a golden opportunity to own a 5 Bedroom home, with a main floor bedroom! Edge of town, sitting on almost a half of an acre of land, is your own personal paradise. Newer furnace & air will leave you with comfort during the hotter or colder temps. Relax on your enclosed wrap around porch & enjoy the large yard for your pets & entertainment. Open staircase only adds to the natural beauty this home has to offer. *March 2025, there will be city water & sewer ran to this property!
